OL,3,CTuk-tuk driver who admitted stealing
OL,4,Cfine wine worth thousands to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, Judge Mark Lucraft KC put
OL,8,Foff his Old Bailey sentence so the
OL,9,Fdefendant could "make good" on his
OL,10,Fpromise to help police recover the
OL,11,Fmissing wine.
OL,13,FThe court heard that some of the stash
OL,14,Fwas found on Kubola when he was
OL,15,Farrested riding a pedicab in the City
OL,16,Fof London in June.
OL,18,FAsked what he intended to do with all
OL,19,Fthe wine he had stolen, he told
OL,20,Fpolice: "The wine is to drink, no?"
