OL,7,FOutlining the facts of the case,
OL,8,Fprosecutor Matthew Jolliffe said the
OL,9,Fdefendant entered Comptoir Cafe and
OL,10,FWine in Mayfair in the early hours of
OL,11,FMay 1 and made off with several
OL,12,Fbottles of wine valued at #6,000 and
OL,13,F#200 cash from the till.
OL,15,FOn May 13, and June 8, he attended
OL,16,FOliveto and Olivo on Elizabeth Street
OL,17,Fin Belgravia and took multiple bottles
OL,18,Fof wine and cash.
