OL,7,FKubola, from Islington, north London,
OL,8,Falso struck three times at Piazza
OL,9,FItaliana on Threadneedle Street in the
OL,10,FCity of London, the court was told.
OL,12,FIn the first incident, Kubola caused
OL,13,Fdamage to an external door and locks,
OL,14,Fcosting #1,000 to change locks and
OL,15,F#425 in repairs.
