OL,7,FMr Jolliffe said: "The defendant used
OL,8,Fa pedal cab to cycle out of the City
OL,9,Fof London. He returned on the same
OL,10,Fpedal cab at 3.35am, loaded a wheelie
OL,11,Fbin into the back and left at 3.57am
OL,12,Fcycling out of the City of London."
OL,14,FAround #100 was taken from the cash
OL,15,Ftill and 73 bottles, at a total
OL,16,Freplacement cost of #23,801, the court
OL,17,Fheard.
