OL,7,FEarly on June 15, he was caught on
OL,8,FCCTV at the restaurant a second time
OL,9,Fand made off with three more bottles
OL,10,Fof wine valued at #680 and #55 from
OL,11,Fthe till.
OL,13,FFour days later, he entered the
OL,14,Fproperty again but left without taking
OL,15,Fanything after the alarm sounded.
OL,17,FHe was arrested on June 22 while
OL,18,Friding the tuk-tuk on Cornhill in the
OL,19,FCity of London.
