OL,3,CTuk-tuk driver who admitted stealing
OL,4,Cfine wine worth thousands to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FHe was found with a bottle of Villa
OL,8,FBucci wine, a bottle of Laurent-
OL,9,FPerrier champagne, a bottle of Jack
OL,10,FDaniels, a half-empty bottle of Shaw
OL,11,Fand Smith chardonnay, and a bottle of
OL,12,Fvodka.
OL,14,FOther items seized included a spanner,
OL,15,Fpliers, screwdrivers, three crowbars
OL,16,Fand an angle grinder.
OL,18,FIn his police interview, the defendant
OL,19,Fdid not dispute any of the allegations.
