OL,3,CTuk-tuk driver who admitted stealing
OL,4,Cfine wine worth thousands to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FHe questioned the value of the wine
OL,8,Ftaken, saying: "It was not that much.
OL,9,FI have had a restaurant in Italy for
OL,10,F20 years. It did not add up to that
OL,11,Fmuch."
OL,13,FAsked what he did for money, he told
OL,14,Fpolice: "If you have cash, you can
OL,15,Fspend it."
OL,17,FIn mitigation, Daisy Kell-Jones said
OL,18,Fthat the defendant had previously
OL,19,Fworked at Oliveto and Piazza Italiana
OL,20,Frestaurants.
