OL,3,CTuk-tuk driver who admitted stealing
OL,4,Cfine wine worth thousands to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FShe told the court: "He was
OL,8,Feffectively not paid and he made the
OL,9,Freckless and stupid decision, rather
OL,10,Fthan confronting the owners of these
OL,11,Frestaurants and asking for his salary,
OL,12,Feffectively decided to go in and take
OL,13,Fthe salary for himself."
OL,15,FMs Kell-Jones said the defendant had
OL,16,Fdisclosed to her that the majority of
OL,17,Fwine was being stored at a wine
OL,18,Fmerchant and restaurant near Aldgate
OL,19,Fand he was "very keen" that it be
OL,20,Freturned.
