OL,7,FShe said: "Mr Kubola recognises he
OL,8,Fshould not have done what he did and
OL,9,Frecognises the loss caused to those
OL,10,Ftwo restaurants and wants to pay them
OL,11,Fback somehow."
OL,13,FJudge Lucraft put off the sentencing
OL,14,Funtil November 3 to give the defendant
OL,15,Fthe chance to "make good" on his
OL,16,Fpromise to return the wine.
