OL,7,FHe said: "I am going to adjourn the
OL,8,Fsentence to permit Mr Kubola to assist
OL,9,Fpolice to recover what was taken. If
OL,10,Fthat has not happened by then, I will
OL,11,Fdraw my own conclusions from that."
OL,13,FThe judge said he would make no
OL,14,Fpromises about the defence plea for
OL,15,FKubola to be given a suspended
OL,16,Fsentence and avoid jail.
OL,18,FKubola, who was assisted by a Romanian
OL,19,Finterpreter, has previous convictions
OL,20,Ffor shoplifting and driving while
OL,21,Fdisqualified and without a licence.
